ship_frigate_combat.png\
enemy_raider_light_combat.png\
\
Backgrounds:\
bg_sector_map_01.png\
bg_system_map_01.png\
bg_planet_hub_01.png\
\
6. UNIQUENESS RULES\
- Every config must have a unique Id\
- No duplicate IDs are allowed\
- Avoid ambiguous IDs\
- Do not use names like:\
  scout\
  laser\
  mainShip\
  Planet-1\
\
7. DATA AND ART LINKING RULE\
Art file names should logically match config IDs.\
\
Examples:\
ItemData.Id = item_med_supplies\
Icon file = icon_item_med_supplies.png\
\
ShipData.Id = ship_scout\
Icon file = icon_ship_scout.png\
Combat sprite = ship_scout_combat.png}